1
00:00:13,350 --> 00:00:18,200
<i>"Vow to You" - Liu Yuning</i>

2
00:00:18,200 --> 00:00:20,360
♫ <i>The flames illuminate the dark night</i> ♫

3
00:00:20,360 --> 00:00:24,380
♫ <i>Silences surrounds the world</i> ♫

4
00:00:24,380 --> 00:00:29,580
♫ <i>The starlight fades away</i> ♫
♫ <i>The living stands in fear</i> ♫

5
00:00:29,580 --> 00:00:32,540
♫ <i>Wake me me up from this nightmare</i> ♫

6
00:00:32,540 --> 00:00:35,740
♫ <i>I see through your blushing</i> ♫

7
00:00:35,740 --> 00:00:38,640
♫ <i>The thought of you in this world urges me to make a decision</i> ♫

8
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:41,780
♫ <i>Entrusted to me the gale and flame</i> ♫

9
00:00:41,780 --> 00:00:47,200
♫ <i>This farewell leaves me in pain</i> ♫

10
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:50,060
♫ <i>I am fearless when I take a drive into the abyss for you</i> ♫

11
00:00:50,060 --> 00:00:53,180
♫ <i>I'll defend death to be with you</i> ♫

12
00:00:53,180 --> 00:00:58,480
♫ <i>Heaven and Earth resonates with the mountains and rivers</i> ♫

13
00:00:58,480 --> 00:01:01,620
♫ <i>The world is untamed and unbridled</i> ♫

14
00:01:01,620 --> 00:01:04,780
♫ <i>Come what may</i> ♫

15
00:01:04,780 --> 00:01:09,980
♫ <i>I am willing to risk my life for you</i> ♫

16
00:01:09,980 --> 00:01:12,960
♫ <i>Let's go stargazing tomorrow</i> ♫

17
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:18,960
♫ <i>I'll never regret my lifelong vow to you</i> ♫

18
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:45,000
<i>[The Starry Love]
[Adapted from "The Starry Love" by Yi Du Jun Hua]</i>

19
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:48,280
<i>[Episode 33]</i>

20
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:51,840
Imperial Father couldn't make it here, but I have you.

21
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:56,480
I have Man Man, Di Lanjue, Zi Wu, Husui, and everyone I cherish here.

22
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:57,940
It's all I need.

23
00:01:57,940 --> 00:02:00,460
It feels as though we were escorted as brides just yesterday.

24
00:02:00,460 --> 00:02:02,480
Time flies.

25
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:04,140
Chaofeng and I got married in dangerous circumstances.

26
00:02:04,140 --> 00:02:05,700
We made the wedding simple.

27
00:02:05,700 --> 00:02:09,320
I'll make sure your wedding is festive is grand.

28
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:12,720
Sister, I want the finest wine of Wangliang City.

29
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:15,120
I want the best beef in the Beast Realm.

30
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:17,320
I want the best snowflake pastry from House of Colors.

31
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:19,500
And the humans' hotpot!

32
00:02:19,500 --> 00:02:21,060
Silly girl.

33
00:02:21,060 --> 00:02:23,660
What kind of bride only thinks about food?

34
00:02:23,660 --> 00:02:26,040
You want hotpot for your wedding?

35
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:27,460
That is outrageous.

36
00:02:27,460 --> 00:02:30,100
I have always been an outrageous person.

37
00:02:31,500 --> 00:02:32,800
- Let's have it here.
- Okay

38
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,680
Let's go.

39
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:35,100
Tan'er, slow down.

40
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:36,120
Watch your steps, Sister.

41
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,520
Be careful.

42
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:39,120
Slowly.

43
00:02:51,775 --> 00:02:55,225
<i>[Double happiness]</i>

44
00:03:06,180 --> 00:03:08,300
Why are you crying?

45
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:13,480
After years of mischief, someone has finally tamed our beloved Tan Tan.

46
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:16,000
How can I not cry?

47
00:03:18,860 --> 00:03:21,140
Why are you crying?

48
00:03:21,140 --> 00:03:25,300
My eldest brother cast away his desires and emotions for his training.

49
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:27,680
Now he is finally freed from his burdens.

50
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:30,120
Of course, it makes me cry.

51
00:03:34,380 --> 00:03:37,500
You two, it's a day of celebration.

52
00:03:37,500 --> 00:03:40,780
Don't cry. Be happy. Put on a smile.

53
00:03:42,660 --> 00:03:45,760
That's right.You look cute when you smile.

54
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:47,460
Smile more!

55
00:04:48,460 --> 00:04:49,500
Everyone is here.

56
00:04:49,500 --> 00:04:51,840
Let the ceremony begin.

57
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:53,220
Come on, Kui'er.

58
00:04:53,220 --> 00:04:55,060
You're her mother figure.

59
00:04:55,060 --> 00:04:56,380
We'll accept your salute.

60
00:04:56,380 --> 00:04:57,820
Not a chance.

61
00:04:57,820 --> 00:05:00,020
Sister, give him a scolding.

62
00:05:01,340 --> 00:05:03,460
I only mean well.

63
00:05:03,460 --> 00:05:06,140
I want you to have a complete ceremony.

64
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:07,560
Old Fifth.

65
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:09,000
My sister-in-law is scary.

66
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,380
I'm glad I married her sister.

67
00:05:10,380 --> 00:05:12,660
As if I'd let you marry Tan'er.

68
00:05:12,660 --> 00:05:14,480
I wouldn't allow it either.

69
00:05:15,380 --> 00:05:17,220
What kind of bride are you?

70
00:05:17,220 --> 00:05:19,920
You put on the wedding gown but not the veil.

71
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,980
And now you're cuddling the groom.

72
00:05:21,980 --> 00:05:24,060
- That is unorthodox.
- Exactly.

73
00:05:24,060 --> 00:05:26,760
The veil is to keep the bride from feeling embarrassed.

74
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:28,160
I don't feel embarrassed.

75
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:32,500
I want everyone to see the happiest moment of Liguang Yetan.

76
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,920
Are you even an immortal?

77
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:37,860
You can spoil her, but there should be a limit.

78
00:05:37,860 --> 00:05:41,380
Pay respect to Heaven and Earth, your parents, and your brother-in-law.

79
00:05:41,380 --> 00:05:43,820
These are the things you must do.

80
00:05:43,820 --> 00:05:45,180
Shut it.

81
00:05:45,180 --> 00:05:47,100
I'm not paying respect to them.

82
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:52,420
Hey. If you won't do any of these, what am I supposed to do as your attendant?

83
00:05:52,420 --> 00:05:54,900
Who says I'm not following the steps?

84
00:05:55,380 --> 00:05:57,060
Come.

85
00:06:00,580 --> 00:06:01,940
I pay respect only to you.

86
00:06:01,940 --> 00:06:03,400
The world is full of perils.

87
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:05,100
Anyone could be a bad guy.

88
00:06:05,100 --> 00:06:07,200
But I will be there for you, in life and in death.

89
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:10,660
That is our promise to grow old together.

90
00:06:10,660 --> 00:06:17,220
I pay respect only to you as well for you risked your life to save me and made me whole again.

91
00:06:17,900 --> 00:06:21,020
In the past, I feared the desires in my heart.

92
00:06:21,020 --> 00:06:23,240
I shut them away from me.

93
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:26,520
You help me realize that everyone is born with desires.

94
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:29,620
Only true love can let them flow.

95
00:06:29,620 --> 00:06:31,719
♫ <i>I see a light in your starry eyes</i> ♫

96
00:06:31,719 --> 00:06:36,480
Husband and wife, bow to each other.

97
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:39,979
♫ <i>As I sing softly, you and I look at each other</i> ♫

98
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:46,619
♫ <i>There is an azure blue ocean over there</i> ♫

99
00:06:46,619 --> 00:06:48,299
♫ <i>With a sparkling wave of light</i> ♫

100
00:06:48,299 --> 00:06:52,759
♫ <i>You said, "Let's hold hand and not let go"</i> ♫

101
00:06:52,759 --> 00:06:54,460
Kiss! <i>Kiss!</i>

102
00:06:54,460 --> 00:06:56,140
<i>Kiss! Kiss!</i>

103
00:06:56,140 --> 00:06:58,160
<i>Kiss! Kiss! Kiss!</i>

104
00:06:58,160 --> 00:07:04,899
♫ <i>Piece by piece, it melts into unrestrained fireworks</i> ♫

105
00:07:04,899 --> 00:07:09,819
♫ <i>Gently flickering, illuminating the Queen of the Night blossoms</i> ♫

106
00:07:09,819 --> 00:07:16,379
♫ <i>Protecting our promise regardless of the faults of fate</i> ♫

107
00:07:16,379 --> 00:07:17,820
My hard work was worth it!

108
00:07:17,820 --> 00:07:21,599
♫ <i>Gorgeous flowers and fire bloom momentarily</i> ♫

109
00:07:21,599 --> 00:07:23,559
♫ <i>It all turned into sweetness</i> ♫

110
00:07:23,559 --> 00:07:28,739
♫ <i>I am you, and you are me</i> ♫

111
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:32,919
♫ <i>As I see the stars fall</i> ♫

112
00:07:32,919 --> 00:07:35,599
♫ <i>It's like the Queen of the Night flowers and fireworks wrapped in countless rainbows</i> ♫

113
00:07:35,599 --> 00:07:36,800
Blessing from the Xia clan.

114
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,760
♫ <i>Smiles blooming into happiness that can't be melt away</i> ♫

115
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:41,260
Eldest Brother, could it be Mother?

116
00:07:41,260 --> 00:07:42,820
Let's go.

117
00:07:42,820 --> 00:07:45,059
♫ <i>It was you</i> ♫

118
00:07:45,059 --> 00:07:48,059
♫ <i>Who sweetened my parched heart</i> ♫

119
00:07:48,059 --> 00:07:55,059
♫ <i>The stars in the eyes of my beloved gleams with sweetness</i> ♫

120
00:07:55,059 --> 00:07:59,580
When immortals complete their weddings in the past, the Xia clan will cast a rainbow bridge in the sky,

121
00:07:59,580 --> 00:08:03,160
and wish for the couple to have love that lasts forever.

122
00:08:04,940 --> 00:08:07,560
Celestial Mother knew today was our wedding.

123
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:11,180
Perhaps she senses it and feels happy for us.

124
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:14,120
She's always treated me like her own.

125
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:17,480
But I could never tell her my true identity.

126
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:20,300
After I got into trouble, she never scolded me.

127
00:08:20,300 --> 00:08:23,570
She even protected me in Ninth Heaven Hall.

128
00:08:23,980 --> 00:08:24,980
♫ <i>It all turned into sweetness</i> ♫

129
00:08:24,980 --> 00:08:27,820
Thank you, Celestial Mother!

130
00:08:27,820 --> 00:08:30,719
♫ <i>I am you, and you are me</i> ♫

131
00:08:30,719 --> 00:08:33,699
♫ <i>As I see the stars fall</i> ♫

132
00:08:33,699 --> 00:08:37,659
♫ <i>It's like the Queen of the Night flowers and fireworks wrapped in countless rainbows</i> ♫

133
00:08:37,659 --> 00:08:43,799
♫ <i>The passion, between you and I will never be forgotten</i> ♫

134
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:46,020
Cheers!

135
00:08:46,020 --> 00:08:47,920
Bottoms up.

136
00:08:51,300 --> 00:08:52,400
Old Fifth.

137
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,520
Sister-in-law.

138
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:55,940
You have a really unconventional wedding.

139
00:08:55,940 --> 00:08:56,880
I am impressed.

140
00:08:56,880 --> 00:08:58,880
I raise a toast to you.

141
00:09:00,060 --> 00:09:04,140
Sister. Is all of this real? Am I dreaming?

142
00:09:04,140 --> 00:09:05,360
My silly Tan'er.

143
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,880
We will always be this happy from now on.

144
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:08,740
Exactly!

145
00:09:08,740 --> 00:09:10,640
Another drink!

146
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:12,420
- Slow down!
- Ease up on the drinking, Tan'er.

147
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:13,140
You're drunk.

148
00:09:13,140 --> 00:09:14,720
I'm not drunk. I can't be drunk just yet.

149
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:17,240
My sister brought this fine wine from Wangliang City for me.

150
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,860
I must drink it. Come on. Cheers!

151
00:09:18,860 --> 00:09:21,520
You're quite a drinker. I'll finish it for you. Give it here.

152
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:22,600
Bottoms up.

153
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,360
Let me grab a few drinks. Stop it.

154
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,860
- Drink up.
- Look at them.

155
00:09:26,860 --> 00:09:28,440
- They look happy.
- Sister, cheers.

156
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,260
Come on.

157
00:09:29,260 --> 00:09:31,000
You're right.

158
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:37,740
Are you going back to the Heavenly Realm soon?

159
00:09:37,740 --> 00:09:40,300
No, I want to stay here and...

160
00:09:42,620 --> 00:09:44,200
I want...

161
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:49,320
I want to spend some time with my sister-in-law and eldest brother.

162
00:09:51,220 --> 00:09:54,440
I used to think of weddings as mere ceremonies.

163
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:57,220
But now that I witnessed their wedding today,

164
00:09:57,220 --> 00:10:04,240
I realized how nice it is to be in love and spend the rest of your life with your loved one.

165
00:10:12,140 --> 00:10:14,060
If you are willing,

166
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:16,980
we can have a life together.

167
00:10:16,980 --> 00:10:21,100
Because... you're always so clumsy. And...

168
00:10:21,100 --> 00:10:22,680
What?

169
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:23,960
No.

170
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,840
I mean...

171
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,440
You're innocent.

172
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:29,360
It's innocence.

173
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:32,600
I want to take care of you.

174
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:36,140
I don't mind being by your side as A'Cai did.

175
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:41,620
I thought you hated to be A'Cai.

176
00:10:41,620 --> 00:10:43,480
As long as you like it.

177
00:10:45,620 --> 00:10:47,340
Actually,

178
00:10:47,340 --> 00:10:53,720
I want to stay here not just for my sister-in-law and eldest brother.

179
00:10:54,460 --> 00:10:56,260
I want to...

180
00:10:58,020 --> 00:11:00,300
stay here with you.

181
00:11:00,300 --> 00:11:02,100
You mean it?

182
00:11:03,220 --> 00:11:04,740
Yes.

183
00:11:39,420 --> 00:11:41,160
I was never a drinker!

184
00:11:41,160 --> 00:11:43,020
So stop drinking.

185
00:11:43,020 --> 00:11:45,760
All right. That's enough.

186
00:11:48,980 --> 00:11:52,480
Tan Tan has her Empyrean Xuanshang.

187
00:11:53,100 --> 00:11:56,700
His Highness has Princess Ziwu.

188
00:11:56,700 --> 00:11:59,780
Sister Qingkui has Prince Chaofeng by her side.

189
00:11:59,780 --> 00:12:02,640
They are all in love.

190
00:12:02,640 --> 00:12:06,820
But I am still alone and single!

191
00:12:06,820 --> 00:12:11,040
<i>It seems I was right to keep you from the truth.</i>

192
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:13,620
I love being alone and single.

193
00:12:13,620 --> 00:12:16,580
I'll do fine by my lonesome.

194
00:12:16,580 --> 00:12:18,280
- I'm happy!
- I can't eat anymore.

195
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:20,280
All right.

196
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:25,000
Thanks to Old Fifth, we have enough men for our armed escort agency.

197
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:28,860
We'll have lots of work to do soon when we're open for business.

198
00:12:28,860 --> 00:12:33,280
I found a spot in your area to set up my clinic.

199
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,460
Don't worry.

200
00:12:34,460 --> 00:12:37,400
You can keep all the money I make.

201
00:12:37,400 --> 00:12:39,380
Keep them yourself.

202
00:12:39,380 --> 00:12:41,020
I have no need for money.

203
00:12:41,020 --> 00:12:42,940
I am all yours too.

204
00:12:57,820 --> 00:12:59,080
See that?

205
00:12:59,080 --> 00:13:01,300
The moon looks beautiful tonight.

206
00:13:01,300 --> 00:13:04,460
It reminds me of the poem you read for me.

207
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:07,020
"Under the moonlight, on Lake Xi, a boat carries us.

208
00:13:07,020 --> 00:13:10,400
Lying enchanted, on the flowers, our night is far from over."

209
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:11,500
What's wrong?

210
00:13:11,500 --> 00:13:13,600
Are you not feeling well again?

211
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,840
No.

212
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:18,620
You admired the moon and the poem,

213
00:13:18,620 --> 00:13:22,040
but do you remember it's our wedding night?

214
00:13:22,040 --> 00:13:24,600
Of course, I remember.

215
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:26,260
So...

216
00:14:13,260 --> 00:14:15,100
Yun'er...

217
00:14:15,100 --> 00:14:16,760
Your Majesty.

218
00:14:16,760 --> 00:14:21,120
Are you ever going to stop looking at the ornate mirror?

219
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:24,000
His Majesty imprisoned me here.

220
00:14:24,820 --> 00:14:26,800
What else can I do?

221
00:14:26,800 --> 00:14:29,000
You have me at your service.

222
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:30,760
You?

223
00:14:31,780 --> 00:14:34,520
I can avenge you.

224
00:14:34,520 --> 00:14:35,800
Why?

225
00:14:35,800 --> 00:14:40,240
My eldest brother and the Second Prince both died in regret.

226
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:41,960
I can't sleep.

227
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:43,980
I can't accept this.

228
00:14:43,980 --> 00:14:46,200
And does it even matter?

229
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:49,610
You can't even defeat Chaofeng.

230
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:53,380
Now, Shaodian Youqin is working with him.

231
00:14:54,380 --> 00:14:57,460
You are only throwing your life away.

232
00:14:57,460 --> 00:15:00,260
I can't kill them.

233
00:15:01,540 --> 00:15:04,700
But I can kill those they love.

234
00:15:05,940 --> 00:15:09,660
I want them to feel our anguish.

235
00:15:09,660 --> 00:15:11,960
Yetan...

236
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:13,980
Qingkui...

237
00:15:13,980 --> 00:15:15,920
Correct.

238
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:26,460
<i>Go.</i>

239
00:15:26,460 --> 00:15:31,900
<i>Carry my hate with you as you tear them into pieces.</i>

240
00:15:33,340 --> 00:15:34,700
<i>Brother.</i>

241
00:15:34,700 --> 00:15:37,160
<i>You may rest in peace now.</i>

242
00:15:37,160 --> 00:15:39,880
<i>I'll make sure they suffer.</i>

243
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:42,825
<i>[To Imperial Father: My wedding with Youqin is complete.]</i>

244
00:15:44,540 --> 00:15:46,120
Great.

245
00:15:46,120 --> 00:15:48,220
Your Majesty looks overjoyed.

246
00:15:48,220 --> 00:15:49,980
Is it because of merriment?

247
00:15:49,980 --> 00:15:51,700
Great merriment!

248
00:15:51,700 --> 00:15:53,240
Look.

249
00:15:55,160 --> 00:15:57,520
I should have your fingers chopped.

250
00:15:57,520 --> 00:15:59,600
I deserve as much!

251
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:03,480
Tan'er and Youqin are finally married.

252
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:05,240
Congratulations, Your Majesty.

253
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:07,140
Congratulations!

254
00:16:07,140 --> 00:16:09,860
Empyrean Xuanshang will take care of Princess Yetan.

255
00:16:09,860 --> 00:16:14,020
Your Majesty, that's a weight lifted off your shoulder.

256
00:16:14,020 --> 00:16:15,840
Indeed.

257
00:16:17,820 --> 00:16:18,750
<i>[Memorial]</i>

258
00:16:20,900 --> 00:16:25,000
Liguang Chiyao has been sending memorials through his former peers.

259
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:27,020
He wants to be reinstated.

260
00:16:27,020 --> 00:16:29,440
He is pestering me.

261
00:16:29,440 --> 00:16:33,120
Your Majesty. The Grand Chancellor has turned over a new leaf.

262
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:37,740
I doubt he will give you or Princess Yetan any trouble.

263
00:16:37,740 --> 00:16:39,580
Fine.

264
00:16:39,580 --> 00:16:42,320
He is my uncle, after all.

265
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:44,860
I'll make him wait for a few days.

266
00:16:44,860 --> 00:16:47,800
I'll send him to the Void as a human ambassador.

267
00:16:47,800 --> 00:16:49,260
I don't feel like seeing him now.

268
00:16:49,260 --> 00:16:50,880
Yes.

269
00:16:51,400 --> 00:16:57,050
<i>[Heartless Escort Agency]</i>

270
00:16:58,200 --> 00:17:00,230
<i>Run!</i>

271
00:17:00,230 --> 00:17:01,950
<i>[Heartless Escort Agency]</i>

272
00:17:08,020 --> 00:17:11,020
It's ready. Don't let it go cold. Eat now.

273
00:17:11,020 --> 00:17:14,140
Thank you for coming here and making us breakfast, Husui.

274
00:17:14,140 --> 00:17:16,020
Sit down and join us.

275
00:17:16,020 --> 00:17:19,940
Sister. I've been craving this for a while. Try it out.

276
00:17:25,360 --> 00:17:26,960
Do you like it?

277
00:17:27,660 --> 00:17:30,480
If you like it, I'll make more tomorrow.

278
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:34,060
Tomorrow I'll be away.

279
00:17:39,190 --> 00:17:40,580
<i>[Heartless Escort Agency]</i>

280
00:17:40,580 --> 00:17:42,640
Heartless Escort Agency.

281
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:46,400
With this, our business will take off!

282
00:17:49,790 --> 00:17:51,720
<i>[Heartless Escort Agency]</i>

283
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:54,460
"Heartless Escort Agency's grand opening."

284
00:17:54,460 --> 00:17:55,440
Have you lost your mind?

285
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:58,840
You used my Assassin Assembly Hall and my nickname!

286
00:17:58,840 --> 00:18:02,220
Your Romantic Heroic Chronicles made waves in the world.

287
00:18:02,220 --> 00:18:05,160
The name "Heartless" guarantees business.

288
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:08,800
I'm your brother-in-law, let me put your name to good use.

289
00:18:08,800 --> 00:18:12,220
Do you want my business to fail?

290
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:16,660
Seeing you're working so hard to give Qingkui a happy life, fine.

291
00:18:16,660 --> 00:18:17,980
It's very honorable of you.

292
00:18:17,980 --> 00:18:19,580
But here's the deal.

293
00:18:19,580 --> 00:18:23,020
You can use my name, but I want half of the profit.

294
00:18:23,020 --> 00:18:25,100
Are you seriously this greedy?

295
00:18:25,100 --> 00:18:27,500
Your bad habit as a soul shard really stuck.

296
00:18:27,500 --> 00:18:28,680
Make it 60 percent.

297
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:30,680
Fine, you get half the profit.

298
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:35,720
But there's a problem. I need more guards.

299
00:18:35,720 --> 00:18:38,020
Could you point some guards here?

300
00:18:38,020 --> 00:18:40,040
Deal. Pour me some tea.

301
00:18:53,260 --> 00:18:57,080
The words just got out, and there's already a crowd.

302
00:18:58,260 --> 00:19:00,240
I should inform them.

303
00:19:06,260 --> 00:19:11,260
Our plan was to lure Shaodian Youqin here and track down the two princesses.

304
00:19:11,260 --> 00:19:14,440
But all we got was this stinking bird.

305
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:16,200
Very well.

306
00:19:17,340 --> 00:19:22,220
The rest of you, stay here and stall Shaodian Youqin.

307
00:19:22,900 --> 00:19:26,740
- You two, come with me.
- Yes.

308
00:19:29,980 --> 00:19:32,180
I can't take it anymore. Stop it. I can't drink anymore.

309
00:19:32,180 --> 00:19:33,400
Just one more cup.

310
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:34,920
- I am stuffed. Stop pouring me tea.
- Just one more cup.

311
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:37,340
No. Stop it!

312
00:19:37,340 --> 00:19:38,540
Stop it.

313
00:19:38,540 --> 00:19:40,680
Empyrean Xuanshang. I need a word with you.

314
00:19:40,680 --> 00:19:42,340
I need your wife tomorrow.

315
00:19:42,340 --> 00:19:44,420
- What for?
- I want her company.

316
00:19:44,420 --> 00:19:46,540
- Whose company do I get?
- She's been with you for days!

317
00:19:46,540 --> 00:19:49,340
Why can't she spend a day with me? I barely remember what she looks like.

318
00:19:49,340 --> 00:19:51,280
She mentioned she was going out.

319
00:19:51,280 --> 00:19:53,520
Are you talking about the same thing?

320
00:19:54,500 --> 00:19:55,640
What is it?

321
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:57,380
I'm not telling you.

322
00:19:57,380 --> 00:20:01,400
By the way, Prince Chaofeng, I just passed by your agency. A dozen of people were waiting.

323
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:02,440
- Really?
- Yes.

324
00:20:02,440 --> 00:20:04,020
I already have customers?

325
00:20:04,020 --> 00:20:05,200
I should go and take a look.

326
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:07,600
My nickname works wonder.

327
00:20:07,600 --> 00:20:09,660
I don't have enough guards.

328
00:20:09,660 --> 00:20:10,960
Old Fifth.

329
00:20:10,960 --> 00:20:13,240
You are getting half of the profit. You must come with me.

330
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:15,560
Wait. I only contribute the name. Why should I work?

331
00:20:15,560 --> 00:20:17,920
- I'm changing the name.
- Let's go.

332
00:20:19,180 --> 00:20:20,420
Kui'er!

333
00:20:20,420 --> 00:20:22,900
Old Fifth and I are going to the agency! We have customers!

334
00:20:22,900 --> 00:20:24,940
- Get your lunch first.
- Never mind.

335
00:20:24,940 --> 00:20:26,500
Don't teach my husband bad stuff.

336
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:27,820
Me?

337
00:20:27,820 --> 00:20:30,040
He's worse than me.

338
00:20:30,040 --> 00:20:32,360
- Let's go.
- Go on.

339
00:20:32,360 --> 00:20:34,360
Stay safe.

340
00:20:37,380 --> 00:20:38,780
Let's go.

341
00:20:57,020 --> 00:20:59,840
Come. Try the fruits our Beast King grew.

342
00:20:59,840 --> 00:21:01,560
- Did you steal these?
- Thanks.

343
00:21:01,560 --> 00:21:02,860
You can't call this stealing.

344
00:21:02,860 --> 00:21:04,980
It's perfectly normal for a bird to gather fruits from the field.

345
00:21:04,980 --> 00:21:07,380
The only difference being these are from the Beast King's field.

346
00:21:07,380 --> 00:21:09,320
Man Man. You should try the pancake I made.

347
00:21:09,320 --> 00:21:10,540
Sure.

348
00:21:10,540 --> 00:21:12,380
Thanks.

349
00:21:15,260 --> 00:21:17,540
Are you going out tomorrow?

350
00:21:17,540 --> 00:21:19,080
I am getting some new clothes.

351
00:21:19,080 --> 00:21:21,680
What's the occasion? Why do you need new clothes?

352
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:24,640
I think it's...

353
00:21:25,300 --> 00:21:27,740
It's just a normal day.

354
00:21:27,740 --> 00:21:30,240
What's so special about tomorrow?

355
00:21:30,240 --> 00:21:31,480
Even I know.

356
00:21:31,480 --> 00:21:32,720
Where are Di Lanjue and Ziwu?

357
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:34,040
Why aren't they with you?

358
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:36,160
They will be here later.

359
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:38,180
They had just fallen in love.

360
00:21:38,180 --> 00:21:39,900
They are now inseparable.

361
00:21:39,900 --> 00:21:42,260
All of you are loving couples.

362
00:21:42,260 --> 00:21:44,760
I'm the only one who can't fit in.

363
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:47,140
And you too, Husui.

364
00:21:47,140 --> 00:21:49,400
You are enjoying your life here.

365
00:21:53,340 --> 00:21:55,520
Zhu Duanshan!

366
00:21:57,540 --> 00:22:00,720
Void Tyrant has declared to let us leave the Void.

367
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:02,360
What are you doing here?

368
00:22:02,360 --> 00:22:04,680
Are you disobeying Void Tyrant's order?

369
00:22:04,680 --> 00:22:06,920
What if I am?

370
00:22:08,020 --> 00:22:09,760
Kill them.

371
00:22:18,140 --> 00:22:19,740
Watch out!

372
00:22:20,860 --> 00:22:22,400
Sister!

373
00:23:27,440 --> 00:23:29,080
Husui!

374
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:49,640
Cursed bird.

375
00:23:58,620 --> 00:24:01,920
Man Man! Man Man!

376
00:24:26,120 --> 00:24:28,320
Your Highness! Your Highness!

377
00:24:28,320 --> 00:24:29,880
Tan'er...

378
00:24:44,780 --> 00:24:47,020
Man Man!

379
00:24:51,580 --> 00:24:53,120
Man Man...

380
00:24:59,820 --> 00:25:02,100
What a nuisance.

381
00:25:05,780 --> 00:25:08,160
Man Man!

382
00:25:12,160 --> 00:25:14,360
Man Man!

383
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:31,360
Man...

384
00:25:45,540 --> 00:25:50,100
I'd love to see the look on Chaofeng and Shaodian Youqin's faces.

385
00:27:11,860 --> 00:27:14,580
<i>That's Dongqiu magic!</i>

386
00:27:25,980 --> 00:27:27,260
Old Fifth. Quick.

387
00:27:27,260 --> 00:27:29,240
Look at the crowd.

388
00:27:35,180 --> 00:27:36,260
They are finally here.

389
00:27:36,260 --> 00:27:37,920
My apologies. Sorry for the wait.

390
00:27:37,920 --> 00:27:40,440
I am the owner of this agency.

391
00:27:40,440 --> 00:27:42,040
It's all right.

392
00:27:42,040 --> 00:27:43,820
We all run major businesses.

393
00:27:43,820 --> 00:27:45,420
We've been waiting for your opening.

394
00:27:45,420 --> 00:27:46,860
We'd like to have a word.

395
00:27:46,860 --> 00:27:49,500
<i>Exactly.</i>

396
00:27:49,500 --> 00:27:52,180
Sure. We'll talk inside. This way.

397
00:27:52,180 --> 00:27:54,640
After you.

398
00:28:10,780 --> 00:28:13,060
Who are you?

399
00:28:13,060 --> 00:28:15,360
<i>Run!</i>

400
00:28:21,320 --> 00:28:22,720
They left without a fight.

401
00:28:22,720 --> 00:28:24,660
Oh, no. They are the decoy.

402
00:28:24,660 --> 00:28:26,120
Let's go.

403
00:28:43,780 --> 00:28:46,280
Grab his hand!

404
00:28:56,260 --> 00:28:58,040
Tan'er!

405
00:29:13,580 --> 00:29:15,200
Tan'er?

406
00:29:21,980 --> 00:29:24,720
I may have failed to kill you,

407
00:29:25,260 --> 00:29:27,920
but you won't live for long.

408
00:29:28,540 --> 00:29:31,280
You have to kill him!

409
00:29:35,100 --> 00:29:36,820
Man Man!

410
00:29:38,620 --> 00:29:39,880
Are you all right?

411
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:41,520
Are you all right?

412
00:29:43,420 --> 00:29:45,940
Sister. Sister, save her now. Sister!

413
00:29:45,940 --> 00:29:47,380
All right.

414
00:29:54,620 --> 00:29:56,100
Sister, save her.

415
00:29:56,100 --> 00:29:58,460
Sister, help her.

416
00:29:58,460 --> 00:29:59,840
Sister...

417
00:29:59,840 --> 00:30:02,100
Sister, you must save her.

418
00:30:02,100 --> 00:30:03,340
Sister...

419
00:30:03,340 --> 00:30:04,960
Tan'er...

420
00:30:06,060 --> 00:30:07,440
Tan Tan...

421
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:09,060
I'm right here. I'm here.

422
00:30:09,060 --> 00:30:10,540
Hang in there.

423
00:30:10,540 --> 00:30:12,800
I know. This is my end.

424
00:30:12,800 --> 00:30:14,320
That's nonsense!

425
00:30:14,320 --> 00:30:15,420
You will live!

426
00:30:15,420 --> 00:30:17,980
I prepared a surprise for you at House of Colors.

427
00:30:17,980 --> 00:30:19,500
You have to be there.

428
00:30:19,500 --> 00:30:21,600
You have to live!

429
00:30:21,600 --> 00:30:24,680
Hang in there, do you hear me?

430
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:28,980
I knew you'd remember.

431
00:30:29,840 --> 00:30:34,440
His Highness sent me as a gift

432
00:30:34,440 --> 00:30:36,560
so I could

433
00:30:37,660 --> 00:30:39,860
make you happy.

434
00:30:39,860 --> 00:30:45,640
But you've brought me more joy.

435
00:30:46,180 --> 00:30:48,380
- Don't say that now.
- Happy...

436
00:30:48,380 --> 00:30:49,940
Don't say that!

437
00:30:49,940 --> 00:30:51,700
Hang in there!

438
00:30:51,700 --> 00:30:55,300
If you die now, I'll never forgive you!

439
00:30:55,300 --> 00:30:59,360
Hang in there!

440
00:31:00,360 --> 00:31:03,780
When you took the Holy Fabric,

441
00:31:03,780 --> 00:31:07,360
you still

442
00:31:07,360 --> 00:31:09,840
owe me a wish.

443
00:31:09,840 --> 00:31:13,020
Yes, I remember that.

444
00:31:13,020 --> 00:31:15,350
Listen to me.

445
00:31:15,860 --> 00:31:17,240
After...

446
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:19,400
After I'm...

447
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:21,840
After I'm gone,

448
00:31:22,940 --> 00:31:26,260
you can only grieve for three days.

449
00:31:26,260 --> 00:31:28,360
After that,

450
00:31:28,360 --> 00:31:31,240
you must be

451
00:31:31,980 --> 00:31:38,160
the carefree little devil you are again.

452
00:31:38,160 --> 00:31:40,540
Don't say that!

453
00:31:40,540 --> 00:31:44,120
Man Man, get up!

454
00:32:03,340 --> 00:32:05,360
Tan Tan...

455
00:32:11,820 --> 00:32:13,740
Man Man!

456
00:32:13,740 --> 00:32:16,240
Man Man...

457
00:32:21,500 --> 00:32:23,800
Man Man!

458
00:32:35,340 --> 00:32:36,800
Did you get him?

459
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:38,400
He got away.

460
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:40,840
Youqin!

461
00:32:40,840 --> 00:32:43,100
Youqin, save her!

462
00:32:43,100 --> 00:32:45,760
Please save her!

463
00:32:45,760 --> 00:32:47,380
Youqin, figure something out!

464
00:32:47,380 --> 00:32:48,940
Let's go.

465
00:32:49,790 --> 00:32:50,940
Save her!

466
00:32:50,940 --> 00:32:54,540
Tan Tan! Did you see that extraordinary magic?

467
00:32:55,100 --> 00:32:56,720
- Man Man!
- Man Man!

468
00:32:56,720 --> 00:33:00,960
Feel her. Feel her.

469
00:33:00,960 --> 00:33:03,140
Her body is still warm.

470
00:33:03,140 --> 00:33:04,680
She can still be saved.

471
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:06,980
Please save her.

472
00:33:07,780 --> 00:33:09,940
Feel her.

473
00:33:09,940 --> 00:33:12,160
Save her.

474
00:33:13,140 --> 00:33:16,840
Eldest Brother, what happened here?

475
00:33:18,440 --> 00:33:21,940
Save her. You must know a way.

476
00:33:21,940 --> 00:33:23,600
Please save her.

477
00:33:23,600 --> 00:33:25,200
Can't you save her?

478
00:33:25,200 --> 00:33:29,020
Save her if you can!

479
00:33:29,020 --> 00:33:31,760
Save her!

480
00:33:32,940 --> 00:33:34,340
Who did this?

481
00:33:34,340 --> 00:33:36,040
Zhu Duanshan.

482
00:33:39,060 --> 00:33:41,460
Was he here for you?

483
00:33:43,160 --> 00:33:45,240
Why aren't you hurt?

484
00:33:47,220 --> 00:33:49,220
Why was Man Man killed instead?

485
00:33:51,400 --> 00:33:52,840
It's my fault.

486
00:33:52,840 --> 00:33:55,180
I thought the Void Empress would relent after she was jailed.

487
00:33:55,180 --> 00:33:58,340
Di Lanjue. They came prepared.

488
00:33:58,340 --> 00:34:00,000
They lured us away.

489
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:01,880
They caught us off guard.

490
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:05,040
Di Lanjue. Calm down.

491
00:34:05,040 --> 00:34:07,740
He never wanted this.

492
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:12,400
Sister-in-law is already heartbroken.

493
00:34:12,400 --> 00:34:15,040
Now is not the time to fight.

494
00:34:27,120 --> 00:34:29,260
I'll save you.

495
00:34:29,260 --> 00:34:31,500
You will be fine.

496
00:34:31,500 --> 00:34:34,940
We should first give Man Man a proper funeral.

497
00:34:34,940 --> 00:34:36,640
As for the rest...

498
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:39,420
We'll discuss it later.

499
00:34:39,420 --> 00:34:44,099
♫ <i>You say, "Light swept through the twin flowers"</i> ♫

500
00:34:44,099 --> 00:34:46,080
You're safe now.

501
00:34:47,350 --> 00:34:51,190
♫ <i>Wandering at the desolate cliff</i> ♫

502
00:34:51,190 --> 00:34:56,419
♫ <i>Whose face has the wind comfort again?</i> ♫

503
00:34:56,419 --> 00:35:03,319
♫ <i>When the seabed sand are flying everywhere</i> ♫

504
00:35:03,319 --> 00:35:09,499
♫ <i>If only I can spend the sorrowful night with you</i> ♫

505
00:35:09,499 --> 00:35:15,399
♫ <i>We'll go through the ups and downs together</i> ♫

506
00:35:15,399 --> 00:35:21,099
♫ <i>Hair being messed up by the misplaced time and space</i> ♫

507
00:35:21,099 --> 00:35:27,779
♫ <i>No matter how tough it is, I'm not afraid</i> ♫

508
00:35:27,779 --> 00:35:33,119
♫ <i>You are the crescent in my heart</i> ♫

509
00:35:33,119 --> 00:35:39,799
♫ <i>My radiant light shining through the years</i> ♫

510
00:35:39,799 --> 00:35:51,179
♫ <i>If I do shed tears, they will turn into flowers in my heart</i> ♫

511
00:35:52,060 --> 00:35:57,319
♫ <i>I'll always be the unchanging love in your heart</i> ♫

512
00:35:57,319 --> 00:36:04,139
♫ <i>Even the galaxy will agree with me, love needs no answer</i> ♫

