<i>He met someone who was there for firewood.</i>

523
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:01,520
<i>That person was Zhong Ziqi.</i>

524
00:37:01,520 --> 00:37:07,480
<i>Upon hearing the melodies of Boya's qin, he said, "As majestic as Mount Tai."</i>

525
00:37:07,480 --> 00:37:11,540
<i>Yu Boya thought, "The message of this tune was about the mountain's view."</i>

526
00:37:11,540 --> 00:37:13,760
<i>So, he played another tune.</i>

527
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:15,660
<i>This time, it's the running river.</i>

528
00:37:15,660 --> 00:37:17,320
<i>Zhong Ziqi heard the tune.</i>

529
00:37:17,320 --> 00:37:20,380
<i>"The roars of a running river."</i>

530
00:37:21,420 --> 00:37:26,240
<i>Whatever tune Yu Boya played, Zhong Ziqi could tell what was going on in his mind.</i>

531
00:37:26,240 --> 00:37:29,520
<i>Hence, the two became close friends.</i>

532
00:37:29,520 --> 00:37:30,720
<i>And then?</i>

533
00:37:30,720 --> 00:37:35,700
<i>And then, Zhong Ziqi passed away.</i>

534
00:37:35,700 --> 00:37:39,480
<i>Yu Boya was very sad. So, he smashed his qin.</i>

535
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:43,060
<i>He swore to never play any music again.</i>

536
00:37:43,060 --> 00:37:47,160
<i>So, the humans have a name for those</i>

537
00:37:47,160 --> 00:37:50,840
<i>who can read our minds: "soulmates."</i>

538
00:37:51,540 --> 00:37:53,840
<i>You always know what I am thinking.</i>

539
00:37:53,840 --> 00:37:55,060
<i>Are you my soulmate?</i>

540
00:37:55,060 --> 00:37:57,280
<i>You are mine too.</i>

541
00:37:57,840 --> 00:38:01,860
<i>From now on, we'll make this day our "Soulmate Day."</i>

542
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:06,200
<i>Wherever we are, we must celebrate this day every year. Alright?</i>

543
00:38:06,200 --> 00:38:08,620
<i>A promise of a lifetime.</i>

544
00:38:08,620 --> 00:38:11,720
<i>- Sealing it.
- Sealing it.</i>

545
00:38:17,820 --> 00:38:21,360
I must bring Man Man back to Mount Cangdan myself.

546
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:23,700
That was her birthplace.

547
00:38:25,100 --> 00:38:26,740
I'm coming with you.

548
00:38:27,180 --> 00:38:28,800
You must not go.

549
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:30,840
Why not?

550
00:38:35,340 --> 00:38:38,000
Is there something you're hiding from me?

551
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:41,380
Why is it I can now absorb turbid air?

552
00:38:42,260 --> 00:38:44,320
I feel different too.

553
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:46,440
What did you do to us?

554
00:38:46,440 --> 00:38:48,620
Your Highnesses. Let's talk in private.

555
00:38:48,620 --> 00:38:51,420
We all trust each other with our lives.

556
00:38:51,420 --> 00:38:53,800
Why can't you say it here?

557
00:38:58,140 --> 00:39:00,340
It wasn't me.

558
00:39:00,340 --> 00:39:03,220
You possessed this power yourselves.

559
00:39:05,020 --> 00:39:09,940
That's because you are the Twin Flower of the Ganoderma Vein.

560
00:39:12,260 --> 00:39:15,240
You're the flower spirits of Dongqiu's sacred tree.

561
00:39:26,060 --> 00:39:27,600
What are you talking about?

562
00:39:27,600 --> 00:39:30,840
How are they even related to that plant of destruction?

563
00:39:30,840 --> 00:39:32,860
Tan'er and I are daughters of humans.

564
00:39:32,860 --> 00:39:34,460
We were born into the human royal family.

565
00:39:34,460 --> 00:39:36,260
How are we flower spirits?

566
00:39:36,260 --> 00:39:37,840
This is nonsense.

567
00:39:37,840 --> 00:39:40,080
Twin Flower of the Ganoderma Vein.

568
00:39:40,780 --> 00:39:42,960
Separated, they absorb pure and turbid air.

569
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:45,000
Together, they can open Guixu and activate the Force of Chaos!.

570
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:48,080
Do you know how serious this accusation is?

571
00:39:48,080 --> 00:39:52,160
The flower spirits were born with such powers, how is that a crime?

572
00:39:52,700 --> 00:39:56,900
Ten millennia ago, the four realms feared them for their power to open Guixu.

573
00:39:56,900 --> 00:39:59,300
So they uprooted the Ganoderma Vein.

574
00:39:59,300 --> 00:40:02,120
The Twin Flower was scattered.

575
00:40:02,740 --> 00:40:04,500
Who would've thought?

576
00:40:04,500 --> 00:40:07,340
The flower spirits were reunited after ten millennia.

577
00:40:07,340 --> 00:40:09,540
They were reincarnated as humans.

578
00:40:09,540 --> 00:40:11,020
All of these...

579
00:40:11,020 --> 00:40:12,740
Not even my father had experienced these.

580
00:40:12,740 --> 00:40:15,000
Why would you, a young girl know about this?

581
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:19,880
Because I witnessed the demise of Dongqiu myself.

582
00:40:36,500 --> 00:40:38,700
<i>The Ganoderma Vein is sacred to Dongqiu!</i>

583
00:40:38,700 --> 00:40:42,580
<i>We will defend it with our lives!</i>

584
00:40:43,340 --> 00:40:47,480
<i>Then we shall destroy Dongqiu!</i>

585
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:50,560
<i>The Twin Flower from the Ganoderma Vein can open Guixu!</i>

586
00:40:50,560 --> 00:40:52,040
<i>That's an ancient legend.</i>

587
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:53,640
<i>No one can prove this claim.</i>

588
00:40:53,640 --> 00:40:56,840
<i>The people of Dongqiu have lived here in peace.</i>

589
00:40:56,840 --> 00:40:58,520
<i>Why would we want to destroy the world?</i>

590
00:40:58,520 --> 00:41:00,420
<i>Please, show us mercy.</i>

591
00:41:00,420 --> 00:41:02,160
<i>Spare our sacred tree.</i>

592
00:41:02,160 --> 00:41:07,460
<i>If the legend is true, the fate of the world is tied to the Ganoderma Vein.</i>

593
00:41:07,460 --> 00:41:09,600
<i>How can we live in peace knowing that?</i>

594
00:41:09,600 --> 00:41:13,480
<i>If the legend is false, the Ganoderma Vein is just a tree.</i>

595
00:41:13,480 --> 00:41:17,580
<i>Why would you sacrifice your lives for a plant?</i>

596
00:41:17,580 --> 00:41:20,220
<i>Stand aside and we shall spare you.</i>

597
00:41:20,220 --> 00:41:24,960
<i>The Ganoderma Vein is connected to the souls of the people of Dongqiu.</i>

598
00:41:24,960 --> 00:41:29,040
<i>Heavenly Emperor and Void Tyrant, if you insist on destroying the sacred tree, then do it over our dead bodies.</i>

599
00:41:29,040 --> 00:41:33,340
<i>We will sacrifice our blood to the spirit of the sacred tree!</i>

600
00:41:36,300 --> 00:41:37,960
<i>Suzhi, hide here and don't come out.</i>

601
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:39,800
<i>- Don't come out.
- Stay here.</i>

602
00:41:39,800 --> 00:41:41,780
<i>Don't come out.</i>

